---
title: Pesto Chicken Traybake and Garlic Rice with roasted pepper and cherry tomatoes
description: The honeyed chicken in this easy traybake recipe is coated in a fresh and herby pesto sauce and served with fluffy garlic rice. Softened peppers and cherry tomatoes add vibrancy and flavour to a simple dish that tastes delish.
